trigger.expression: {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.cpu1.temp.last()}>70 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.cpu2.temp.last()}>70
trigger.name: CPU temperature critical on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.MEMA.last()}>70 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.MEMB.last()}>70 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.MEMC.last()}>70 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.MEMD.last()}>70 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.MEME.last()}>70 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.MEMF.last()}>70 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.MEMG.last()}>70 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.MEMH.last()}>70
trigger.name: DIMM temperature critical on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.FAN1.last()}>9000 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.FAN1.last()}<100 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.FAN2.last()}>9000 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.FAN2.last()}<100 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.FAN3.last()}>9000 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.FAN3.last()}<100 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.FAN4.last()}>9000 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.FAN4.last()}<100
trigger.name: Fan critical on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.PSU1Power.last()}<1 or {IPMI Fujitsu RX2530 M2:ipmi.PSU1Power.last()}<1
trigger.name: Power supply issue on {HOSTNAME}
